			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Riceplz is right , dump all your points into STA because it really wouldn't matter until about Level 20 when your damage caps are gone . That's when you would start buying STR+ and AC+ Items.<BR>
1. AC - To get his LESS .<BR>
2. STR - To hit harder .<BR>
3. STA - To have more HP .<BR>
I'm sure that's the goal of everyone who is making a war. Get hit less but deal alot of damage. But when you do get hit you can take that hit. and well about AGI and DEX <BR>
4. DEX - How many times you do Crippling Blows, Criticals, make weapons proc ect.<BR>
5. AGI - Affects AC, and how many times your dodge, parry, etc.(Not sure on that one.)<BR>
But I found Gnomes to be a really great warrior to. Not to say that there is a BEST warrior class. But still, I found that it's how you play your char. and what's to your liking. Don't play a Barbarian Warrior just because everyone else is, or that you were pressured to do. It's your game.
				</font>
