				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok, now i have figured this out a bit. Because i have a 53 halfling warrior.<BR>
You might think &quot;Oh halfling is weak, let's dump all the points into strength.&quot;<BR>
That is a mistake. Near the endgame (50+) it is insanely easy to boost your str over 200.<BR>
Some people dump all the points into agility. Mistake also.<BR>
The MOST important stat for a warrior of an early level is stamina. It won't look like much of a differince in the earlier levels. But at 50+ ogres/trolls will start having about 500-600 more hps than you. Oh well...<BR>
I like halflings better~ kaka!
				</font>
